data.description: This immaculate Kingfield 3 bedroom has it all! The roof and Leaf Guard gutters were replaced last year.  Newer appliances and heating/Ac, water heater.  Close to park, bus line and local restaurants.  Vaulted ceiling, a large finished basement, and beautiful 3 season porch are just a few amenities that make this house so special.
data.whatILove: This is a charming home in a great neighborhood and has been immaculately cared for.  All newer appliances, newer heating and central air, new roof with a transferable warranty, a three season porch, and more.    Even the playhouse in the backyard has matinence free siding. This house looks small from the front but the interior boasts a vaulted ceiling and a huge family room.
